metadata.name: XO: Party vs Party
metadata.description:
XO: Party vs Party is a tic-tac-toe game between two DAOs. It's the first PartyDAO-native game. All proceedings from the NFT sales will go directly to the game prize pool. The NFT can only be minted while the game is active.

See https://xo.w1nt3r.xyz/ and 0x00110E858e71B69c154C2cD1b9cf151C02A1Bc21
